app_details.title: Injector Origin
app_details.description: Injector Origin is more than just an injector app. Dive into our hero guides, packed with valuable tips and tricks to master every hero's abilities and strategies. Elevate your skills and enhance your gaming experience with Injector Origin now!

reviews.content: At first Id rate it 5 Stars but the more I use it, the more I encountered bugs that really affected me for it to be just a star. The way the app injects things in mlbb files are missing instead of the skin and effects appear at your POV nothing happens at all, and some of the heroes are out model inside the app so if you downloaded the backup you'll get the resources of the old hero instead causing them to be T posing in match its hilarious but stupid. And the one u injected suddenly dissapears
reviews.replyContent: Thank you for your feedback! We’re sorry to hear about these issues. It would help us a lot if you could specify which heroes, skins, or upgrades are causing the problems. We're already working on fixes and appreciate your patience as we improve the app.
